name: Ritz Classic Margao

reviews.review_text:
Starting off, the ambience of this place is pleasant as it's spacious and has plenty of seating arrangements available but gets crowded in no time. Coming to the food, we savoured the Ritz Special Fish Thalli, Prawn Tempura Roll, Coriander Chicken and a few other dishes, but the standout for me was the Fish Thalli which is priced at around
Rs. 314/- respectively and for that number, it's value for money. Service is decent and pricing is reasonable. Definitely check this place out !!!

If u love food, can't miss this place in a Goa trip. Saying RITZ CLASSIC is a cult for authentic Goan food would not b an overstatement.
Offers both veg & Non veg delicacies. If u r lucky as we were, u can also have company of a No of celebrities as well.
Goan Fish Thali was super hit, Chicken Cafarel with goan bread basket accompanied with butter milk :p was heavenly!

Good ambience... Good experience... Quick service... Tasty food... Overall awesome... Awesome decor... Peaceful and quiet... Although it gets crowded pretty quick... And yet you can enjoy your meal peacefully...

description:
### Ritz Classic Margao: A Culinary Gem in Navelim Camp, Goa

Tucked away in the vibrant locale of Navelim Camp, Ritz Classic Margao has garnered an impressive **4.4-star rating** from **4,648 patrons**, establishing itself as a must-visit destination for food enthusiasts. The restaurant is notably celebrated for its **fish thali** and **Goan fish** dishes, alongside a noteworthy sushi selection that further expands its culinary repertoire. With tags reflecting its standout offerings—**275 mentions of restaurant manager, 114 for fish thali, 76 for Goan fish, and 51 for sushi**—it's clear that this spot has made a significant mark on the local dining scene.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Ritz Classic Margao, guests are greeted by a spacious and welcoming atmosphere, amplified by an array of comfortable seating arrangements that cater to both large groups and intimate dining experiences. The decor strikes a balance between traditional Goan aesthetics and modern comfort, with vibrant hues and tasteful embellishments. According to reviews, while the atmosphere is generally peaceful, it does fill up swiftly, creating a lively, bustling vibe as patrons savor their meals. The ambiance is further enhanced by the subtle background music that complements the dining experience without overpowering conversation.

![Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnxcVfEuKYwUfJ-CJI5J3TJ5-z-NUfVYUimNAM8fbPcsTyI6BMJwfR8b7X3QWTOOnWycSHntjrqtBLVGS0s5QSYkxq1Yvae1tis-NoOi8ucFcIzL40n1cIxoMISduciKnmsd8lN=w375-h563-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Ritz Classic Margao is especially famed for its **signature dish**, the **Ritz Special Fish Thali**, a symphony of flavors that has earned its place atop customer favorites. This dish is celebrated not only for its taste but also for its affordability—the price point of approximately **Rs. 314** is mentioned as an incredible value. The **Prawn Tempura Roll** and **Coriander Chicken** are also highlighted, showcasing the restaurant's versatility. Reviewers have described their dining experiences as nothing short of **heavenly**, especially when paired with Goan specialties like **Chicken Cafarel** served alongside a traditional Goan bread basket topped with buttermilk—a perfect pairing for those longing for authenticity.

![Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdleYj4sn1_p_YhaOLoEbDZJgZZvpbFS2sZA0C_QVcJVEmrzYuloHCQXotVdnh97wbQh2yz8mltH0H5b5WDQrEhcKfvsFvpil0Vl5fbuKrxb_0VbNdXjfzK1uxamZgc9z3eC2DpI=w375-h563-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Customer feedback consistently praises the **quick service** and friendly demeanor of the staff, contributing to an overall positive dining experience. While the restaurant is known to be busy, guests have noted that the efficiency of the service ensures that waits are minimal, allowing for a seamless experience all around. The blend of professionalism and warmth from the staff elevates the visit, making patrons feel welcomed and well-cared for. Reservations are recommended due to the restaurant’s popularity, especially during peak dining hours.

### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz surrounding Ritz Classic Margao is palpable, with passionate endorsements from diners recommending it as a **cultural landmark for authentic Goan cuisine**. Many reviews reflect a shared sentiment that it is a must-visit when in Goa, not just for the food but for the chance encounters with various celebrities who occasionally dine there—a testament to its status. Social media is ripe with images of the vibrant dishes, contributing to its growing popularity as a gastronomic destination in Goa.

![Food on Display](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmEoVmMsB4jNMGXSeLTiJIOV4AGFtngvXtJB9NhLSSt8LH66_7atCsPgg7UjA5L2TluPfONiupt9vuLAYXQY-iGoU3N9xEEB-y8jzt_l5g-hRAquezxssakNyFdL5Zo-k8nOuDXlA=w375-h281-p)

Ritz Classic Margao encapsulates the essence of Goan culinary heritage while offering a friendly and enjoyable dining experience. Whether you are a local or just visiting Goa, indulging in their fish thali is an experience not to be overlooked. The combination of delightful dishes, a lively yet comfortable atmosphere, and attentive service makes it a standout choice for anyone seeking a transformative culinary journey.
